<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(ثَانِيهَا)</span> : مَا يَجُوزُ بِغَلَبَةِ الظَّنِّ قَطْعًا وَهُوَ السَّفَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(ثَالِثُهَا)</span> : مَا فِيهِ خِلَافٌ وَالْأَصَحُّ جَوَازُهُ وَهُوَ الْمُفْلِسُ إذَا ظَهَرَتْ أَمَارَاتُ الْإِفْلَاسِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(الثَّالِثُ)</span> : يَنْقَسِمُ أَيْضًا لِمَا هُوَ لِحَقِّ نَفْسِهِ وَهُوَ حَجْرُ الصَّبِيِّ <span class="c2">(وَالْمَجْنُونِ)</span> وَالسَّفِيهِ وَمَا لِحَقِّ الْغَيْرِ وَهُوَ أَنْوَاعٌ:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهَا:</span> حَجْرُ الْمُفْلِسِ لِلْغُرَمَاءِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِي:</span> الرَّاهِنُ لِلْمُرْتَهِنِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثُ:</span> الْمَرِيضُ لِلْوَرَثَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعُ:</span> الْعَبْدُ لِسَيِّدِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الْخَامِسُ:</span> الْمُرْتَدُّ لِلْمُسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسُ:</span> الْحَجْرُ لِلْغَرِيبِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعُ:</span> إذَا امْتَنَعَ مَعَ الْيَسَارِ مِنْ الْبَيْعِ <span class="c2">(لِوَفَاءِ)</span> الدَّيْنِ فَلِلْحَاكِمِ الْحَجْرُ عَلَيْهِ بِالْتِمَاسِ الْغُرَمَاءِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الثَّامِنُ:</span> الْحَجْرُ عَلَى الْمُكَاتَبِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">التَّاسِعُ:</span> الْحَجْرُ عَلَى الْمَالِكِ فِي الْعَبْدِ الْجَانِي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">الْعَاشِرُ:</span> الْحَجْرُ عَلَى الْمَالِكِ قَبْلَ إخْرَاجِ الزَّكَاةِ وَعَلَى الْوَارِثِ فِي التَّرِكَةِ قَبْلَ (وَفَاءِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>